dc_title_s: Wisconsin Leaf-Off Digital Orthophoto Web Map
dc_description_s: Web map displaying WI DNR's Wisconsin Leaf-Off Digital Orthophotography imagery layer along with an index layer.  This map can be used to identify the year and resolution of each county's imagery in this image service, or as a starting point to create a new map.  To open the web map from DNR's GIS Open Data Portal, click the View Metadata: link to the right of the description, then click Open in Map Viewer.*Note that this web map only contains DOPs that Wisconsin DNR has permission to display on a web map.  Some counties may have newer DOPs.
